Chandler, 16702 votes for Gamaliel Painter, 16695 votes for Josiah Hubbard, 16687 votes for Elias Stevens, 16688 votes for James D. Butler, 16677 votes for John Ellsworth, 16670 votes for Zerah Willoby, 16665 votes for Nicholas Bayliss, 16663 votes for Moses Robinson, 16659 votes for Solomon Miller, 16571 votes for Daniel Dana and 16508 votes for William Hall, Jr.
